io.ktor.content

接口 Resource

  • 所有已知实现类:
    JarFileContent, LocalFileContent, URIFileContent

    public Resource

    Represents a resource that can be mixed into OutgoingContent to give more information about content.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static class  Resource.DefaultImpls
      Represents a resource that can be mixed into OutgoingContent to give more information about content.

    • 方法详细资料

      • getContentType

        io.ktor.http.ContentType getContentType()

        Specifies ContentType for this resource.

      • getContentLength

        java.lang.Long getContentLength()

        Specifies content length in bytes for this resource.

        If omitted the resources will be sent as Transfer-Encoding: chunked

      • getVersions

        java.util.List<io.ktor.content.Version> getVersions()

        Provides list of interface Version objects which can be utilized by ConditionalHeaders and PartialContent features.

        另请参阅:
        interface Version, ConditionalHeaders, PartialContent

        Specifies caching policy for this resource

        Provides default implementation of headers property for instance of OutgoingContent
